data.description: Wow, Check out this stunning 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom ranch style home with 3,000+ ft.² of total living space.  You'll love the modern finishes and sprawling floor plan. The kitchen features white shaker cabinets, quartz tops, apron sink and newer stainless appliances. The large family room opens to the kitchen providing the perfect space for family gatherings and  entertaining. The master bedroom has an attached en suite with double vanity, tiled shower, walk-in closet and french doors leading to the large multi tiered deck.  The new roof, kitchen, bathrooms, carpeting, laminate flooring and lighting throughout are just a few of the recent updates.  The finished basement with rec room and bar area provides lots of additional space for entertaining or storage. Plus this home features a two car attached garage and fenced yard. A Great location with easy on/off freeway access and Elms Park just down the street. A definite must see!
